p: I. W. H. Bush Sheriff of Chehalis County Washington Territory do hereby certify that I served that writ of Habeas Corpus of which the within is a true and correct copy to the delivering to and Leaving with one Levicy Hume wife of William Hume and daughter of Levicy O Hamilton a person over the age of 16 years of age and of suitable age, at the residence of the Respondent named in said writ, Levicy O Hammilton the said original writ of Habeas Corpus, not being able to find said Levicy O Hamilton, said respondent said service being made on the 17th day of September AD 1888
In the matter of the application of Maria K. Peterson for writs of Habeas Corpus
Writ directed to Levicy O. Hamilton
I certify that the within is a true copy of the original writ as received by me
WH Bush Sheriff of Chehalis County
